{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017eK5uNTrV4u8XfgoEQDwhd","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Implementation History — 100-close-call\n     2→\n     3→Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4→attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5→of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Iteration 1 — Verify pyth.rs parser compatibility\n    10→\n    11→**Item**: [on-chain] Verify `pyth.rs` parser works with Pyth push oracle price accounts on devnet\n    12→\n    13→**Result**: PASS — no changes needed.\n    14→\n    15→**Findings**:\n    16→- `pyth.rs` Borsh deserialization matches real PriceUpdateV2 account layout (discriminator + write_authority + VerificationLevel enum + PriceFeedMessage + posted_slot)\n    17→- Devnet push oracle accounts use `Full` verification level (1-byte variant), matching the test mock's 133-byte buffer\n    18→- BTC/USD feed ID confirmed: `e62df6c8b4a85fe1a67db44dc12de5db330f7ac66b72dc658afedf0f4a415b43`\n    19→- **Devnet BTC/USD price account**: `4cSM2e6rvbGQUFiJbqytoVMi5GgghSMr8LwVrT9VPSPo` (PDA from Pyth Push Oracle program `pythWSnswVUd12oZpeFP8e9CVaEqJg25g1Vtc2biRsT`, shard 0)\n    20→- Account owner: `rec5EKMGg6MxZYaMdyBfgwp4d5rB9T1VQH5pJv5LtFJ` (Pyth Solana Receiver)\n    21→- No mock format changes needed; `anchor build` + all 20 bankrun tests pass\n    22→\n    23→## Iteration 1 — 2026-03-17T18:46:14Z — OK\n    24→- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n    25→\n    26→## Iteration 2 — Anchor client + game-engine integration\n    27→\n    28→**Item**: [engine] Copy closecall IDL/types into anchor-client, add barrel exports, add CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID\n    29→\n    30→**Result**: PASS\n    31→\n    32→**Changes**:\n    33→- Copied `solana/target/idl/closecall.json` → `packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json`\n    34→- Copied `solana/target/types/closecall.ts` → `packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.ts`\n    35→- Updated `packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts`: added `ClosecallIDL` JSON import, `Closecall` type export, IDL re-export\n    36→- Created `packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`: `CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID` (from IDL address), `getCloseCallRoundPda()`, `getCloseCallConfigPda()`\n    37→- Updated `packages/game-engine/src/index.ts`: added closecall exports\n    38→\n    39→**Notes**:\n    40→- Spec said `packages/config/` but that package only has build configs (tsconfig, eslint). Program IDs live in `packages/game-engine/src/` per existing coinflip/lordofrngs pattern. Followed actual codebase pattern.\n    41→- `pnpm lint` (18 packages): 0 errors, only pre-existing warnings\n    42→- `pnpm typecheck` (18 packages): 0 errors\n    43→\n    44→## Iteration 2 — 2026-03-17T18:51:24Z — OK\n    45→- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n    46→\n    47→## Iteration 3 — Backend account decoders\n    48→\n    49→**Item**: [backend] Add `DecodedCloseCallRound` and `DecodedCloseCallConfig` interfaces + decoder functions\n    50→\n    51→**Result**: PASS\n    52→\n    53→**Changes**:\n    54→- `services/backend/src/worker/account-decoder.ts`:\n    55→  - Added `ClosecallIDL` import from `@rng-utopia/anchor-client`\n    56→  - Instantiated `closecallCoder` BorshAccountsCoder\n    57→  - Added `closeCallPhaseToNumber()` helper (Open=0, Settled=1, Refunded=2)\n    58→  - Added `outcomeToNumber()` helper (Pending=0, Green=1, Red=2, Refund=3)\n    59→  - Added `DecodedCloseCallRound` interface (16 fields: roundId, server, phase, greenEntries, redEntries, greenPool, redPool, openPrice, openPriceExpo, closePrice, createdAt, bettingEndsAt, resolveDeadline, outcome, totalFee, bump)\n    60→  - Added `DecodedCloseCallConfig` interface (7 fields: authority, treasury, pythFeedId, bettingWindowSecs, maxEntriesPerSide, paused, bump)\n    61→  - Added `decodeCloseCallRound()` and `decodeCloseCallConfig()` functions with bnToBigInt conversion and enum mapping\n    62→  - Added